  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Danwatch - &quot;Investigate&quot; 2020-2022</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Journalistic documentation and coverage is increasingly an important tool in the struggle for democratic development and rights violations. That demands strong CSOs and a free press that are capable of gathering solid documentation and getting access to information. Solid documentation and media coverage is for civil society both effective and necessary when addressing rights violations or environmental issues. Both in regards to policy, advocacy and dialogue with stakeholders, as well as in regards to informing the public. But often CSOs and local media are without sufficient capacity to document violations against their fundamental freedom and rights.</narrative>
  </description>
